      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/zimbabwe-nigeria-among-african-central-banks-stepping-in-to-prop-up-currencies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[非洲各国的中央银行正在加大对市场的不协调干预，以支撑其不断下跌的货币并抑制输入性通胀。]]></description>
